| QA-006 | Empty message | Validation prompts user to enter a message. | Prompt displayed correctly. | ✅ Pass |
| QA-007 | Very long message | Chatbot processes request without crashing. | Stable response generated. | ✅ Pass |
| QA-008 | Multiple consecutive questions | Context maintained correctly. | Conversation remained consistent. | ✅ Pass |

