# Issues Identified

## Issue 1

### Observation

When users ask unsupported questions, the chatbot simply states it cannot help.

### Severity

🟡 Low

### Recommendation

Provide alternative resources or suggest contacting customer support.

---

## Issue 2

### Observation

Very long responses occasionally repeat information.

### Severity

🟢 Low

### Recommendation

Reduce repetition and summarize lengthy answers more effectively.

